1533
01:09:06,976 --> 01:09:10,571
Yes. It's too bad
it's so small.

1534
01:09:10,646 --> 01:09:12,045
Small?

1535
01:09:12,114 --> 01:09:14,605
Well, actually,
it's big, isn't it?

1536
01:09:14,683 --> 01:09:16,378
It's a big table, so...

1537
01:09:16,452 --> 01:09:18,682
