for one more.

1538
01:09:18,754 --> 01:09:21,518
Oh, well, if it's not
an imposition...

1539
01:09:21,590 --> 01:09:22,887
Oh... oh.

1540
01:09:22,958 --> 01:09:25,518
Well, let me just go check
if there's enough food.

