1604
01:12:00,249 --> 01:12:02,046
[Sighs]

1605
01:12:02,117 --> 01:12:03,175
Nothing, sir.

1606
01:12:03,252 --> 01:12:05,345
Oh.

1607
01:12:06,922 --> 01:12:08,253
Oh, this food
is so delicious.

1608
01:12:08,324 --> 01:12:09,382
Serves him right, anyway,

1609
