1626
01:12:58,841 --> 01:13:01,036
Well, good, then.

1627
01:13:01,110 --> 01:13:03,237
Enjoy.

1628
01:13:03,312 --> 01:13:05,075
Oh, just one moment.

1629
01:13:05,147 --> 01:13:06,705
Uh, you know, uh,

1630
01:13:06,782 --> 01:13:10,240
